What will happen if you choose to withdraw from the research study at any time?
A) You will be required to pay a penalty fee for early withdrawal; 
B) You will continue to be part of the study but will not receive any further treatments;
C) You may stop participating and this will not affect your future care at Mayo Clinic;
D) Your health insurance will be cancelled as a result of your withdrawal.

Correct answer: C

