A) Only the Principal Investigator and the research team at Mayo Clinic;
B) The research sponsor, the Mayo Clinic Institutional Review Board, and other regulatory agencies;
C) Only you and your personal doctor;
D) Public databases accessible via the internet without any restrictions.

Correct answer: B
